    "content": "<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">招商说明：</span></strong><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\"><br />1.</span><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">计生情趣类目下电击类、窒息类、禁锢类（如贞操锁）、致昏迷类产品暂不招商。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">2.</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">非械字号，卖点具有治疗效果的产品暂不招商。</span> </span></p>\n<table class=\"MsoNormalTable\" style=\"width: 100.0%; background: white; border-collapse: collapse; border: none;\" border=\"1\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr style=\"height: 17.5pt;\">\n<td style=\"width: 12.56%; border: solid windowtext 1.0pt; background: #C00000; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 17.5pt;\" width=\"12%\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; text-align: center; line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: white;\">一级类目</span></strong></span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 16.66%; border: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-left: none; background: #C00000; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 17.5pt;\" width=\"16%\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; text-align: center; line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: white;\">二级类目</span></strong></span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 27.78%; border: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-left: none; background: #C00000; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 17.5pt;\" width=\"27%\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; text-align: center; line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: white;\">行业资质</span></strong></span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 43.0%; border: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-left: none; background: #C00000; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 17.5pt;\" colspan=\"2\" width=\"43%\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; text-align: center; line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: white;\">特殊资质及要求</span></strong></span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 1.0pt;\">\n<td style=\"width: 12.56%; border: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-top: none; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 1.0pt;\" rowspan=\"10\" nowrap=\"nowrap\" width=\"12%\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; text-align: center; line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: white; font-size: 10pt;\">医疗保健</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 16.66%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 1.0pt;\" nowrap=\"nowrap\" width=\"16%\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; text-align: center; line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">保健器械</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 27.78%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 1.0pt;\" rowspan=\"7\" width=\"27%\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">1.</span><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">经营一类医疗器械：营业执照经营范围需包含一类医疗器械/医疗器械生产备案。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">2.</span><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">经营二类器械：具备《二类医疗器械经营备案证》（经营方式需包含零售）/《医疗器械生产许可证》。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">3.</span><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">经营三类器械：具备《医疗器械经营许可证》（经营方式需包含零售）</span><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">/</span><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">《医疗器械生产许可证》。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">4.</span><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">医疗器械网络销售备案凭证（待入驻复审通过后再行申报办理），京东《医疗器械网络交易服务第三方平台备案凭证》见</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\"><a style=\"color: blue; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://pro.jd.com/mall/active/36mqawDTyFwQpodmiJGf6bvPA8hs/index.html\"><span style=\"line-height: 200%;\">链接</span></a></span><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 20.82%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 1.0pt;\" rowspan=\"3\" width=\"20%\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; text-align: center; line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: white; font-size: 10pt;\">/</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 22.18%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 0cm 0cm 0cm; height: 1.0pt;\" rowspan=\"10\" width=\"22%\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: white;\">1. TM</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: white;\">标入驻开店要求注册申请时间至开店审核时间必须大于3个月，TM标有效期请填写申请日期加2年后的日期，R标有效期按商标注册证有效日期填写。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: white;\">2.</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: white;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">专卖店、专营店接受3级以内授权（含3级）。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: white;\">3.</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: white;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: white;\">报关单（经营进口商品）：近两年内的中华人民共和国海关进口货物报关单，报关单上应展现对应品牌名称及商品名称。</span></span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 1.0pt;\">\n<td style=\"width: 16.66%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 1.0pt;\" nowrap=\"nowrap\" width=\"16%\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; text-align: center; line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">护理护具</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 1.0pt;\">\n<td style=\"width: 16.66%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 1.0pt;\" nowrap=\"nowrap\" width=\"16%\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; text-align: center; line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">视力保健</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 1.0pt;\">\n<td style=\"width: 16.66%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 1.0pt;\" nowrap=\"nowrap\" width=\"16%\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; text-align: center; line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">计生情趣</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 20.82%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 1.0pt;\" width=\"20%\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">经营男用延时产品提供符合</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\"><a style=\"color: blue; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=4629\">《京东外用延时剂产品质量标准》</a></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">的检测报告，无需提供《消毒产品生产企业卫生许可证》、《卫生安全评价报告》。</span></span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 16.66%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: 1pt solid windowtext; border-right: 1pt solid windowtext; padding: 0cm 5.4pt;\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; text-align: center; line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">中医健康</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 20.82%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: 1pt solid windowtext; border-right: 1pt solid windowtext; padding: 0cm 5.4pt;\" rowspan=\"3\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; text-align: center; line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: white; font-size: 10pt;\">/</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 1.0pt;\">\n<td style=\"width: 16.66%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 1.0pt;\" nowrap=\"nowrap\" width=\"16%\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; text-align: center; line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">医用护理用品</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 16.66%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\" width=\"16%\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; text-align: center; line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">体外检测试纸/试剂</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 14.5pt;\">\n<td style=\"width: 16.66%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 14.5pt;\" nowrap=\"nowrap\" width=\"16%\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; text-align: center; line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">酵素</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 27.78%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 14.5pt;\" rowspan=\"3\" width=\"27%\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; text-align: center; line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: white; font-size: 10pt;\">《食品经营许可证》/预包装食品经营备案/《食品生产许可证》</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 20.82%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 14.5pt;\" rowspan=\"3\" width=\"20%\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; text-align: center; line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: white; font-size: 10pt;\">/</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 14.5pt;\">\n<td style=\"width: 16.66%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 14.5pt;\" nowrap=\"nowrap\" width=\"16%\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; text-align: center; line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: white; font-size: 10pt;\">减肥塑身</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 14.5pt;\">\n<td style=\"width: 16.66%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 14.5pt;\" nowrap=\"nowrap\" width=\"16%\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; text-align: center; line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; font-size: 10pt;\">药食同源</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 14.5pt;\">\n<td style=\"width: 100.0%; border: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-top: none; padding: 0cm 0cm 0cm 0cm; height: 14.5pt;\" colspan=\"5\" width=\"100%\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 200%; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">1.</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">旗舰店授权书模板：</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\"><a style=\"color: blue; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://helpcenter.jd.com/vender/issue/926-4279.html\">旗舰店授权书模板</a></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 200%; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">2.</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">卖场店授权书模板：</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\"><a style=\"color: blue; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://helpcenter.jd.com/vender/issue/1000-44485.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">卖场店授权模板</a></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 200%; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">3.</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">京东开放平台各类目资费一览表：</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\"><a style=\"color: blue; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=638209647311982592&amp;type=0&amp;btype=1\">京东开放平台类目资费规则</a></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; line-height: 200%; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">4.</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">店铺命</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">名规则：<a style=\"color: blue; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=2598\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=2598</a></span></span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; line-height: 200%; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">附则</span></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; line-height: 200%; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">1.</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">京东商家的行为，发生在本管理规则生效之日以前的，适用当时的规则。发生在本管理规则生效之日以后的，适用本规则。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; line-height: 200%; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">2.</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">京东可根据平台运营情况随时调整本管理规则并以公告的形式向商家公示。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; line-height: 200%; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">3.</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">商家应遵守国家法律、行政法规、部门规章等规范性文件。对任何涉嫌违反国家法律、行政法规、部门规章等规范性文件的行为，本规则已有规定的，适用于本规则。本规则尚无规定的，京东有权酌情处理。但京东对商家的处理不免除其应承担的法律责任。商家在京东的任何行为，应同时遵守与京东及其关联公司签订的各项协议。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; line-height: 200%; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">4.</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">本规则标准于2025年1月23日修订，于2025年1月30日生效。</span></span></p>",
